description:
OneAutomata Log Client is the latest Logging library that supports centralized logging. Write logs that include attachments, write performance logs, exceptions, trace logs, request logs and so much more to a central location for viewing and filtering. Works with OneAutomata Cloud account (FREE), OneAutomata Web application (FREE), and OneAutomata OfflineViewer (FREE).

Use OneAutomata Cloud or Web to store and view logs. Host Logging in a centralized location, gather log files, data, and event logs from different applications and servers.
releaseNotes:
Download OneAutomata Web or Offline Log Viewer 3.1.1 for latest release.
Database upgrade scripts available for older versions: http://www.oneautomata.com/Help/
